          <title>Man tackled after spraying Rep. Omar at town hall</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A man sprayed an unknown substance on U.S. Rep. Ilhan Omar before being tackled to the ground during a town hall she was hosting in Minneapolis on Tuesday evening. Preliminary reports indicate it was not toxic. Minneapolis police are now referring all questions around the attack to the FBI.]]></description>
